---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import SwiperComponent from "../../components/Swiper.astro";
---

<Layout title="Swiper">
	<div class="container">
		<section class="section">
			<p>The Swiper component creates beautiful image carousels with smooth transitions and responsive navigation. Perfect for showcasing portfolios, product galleries, testimonials, or any visual content that needs interactive browsing.</p>
			
			<h2>Demo</h2>
			<div class="component-demo">
				<h3>Product Showcase</h3>
				<SwiperComponent
					slides={[
						{ 
							src: "https://placehold.co/800x500/3b82f6/ffffff?text=Product+1", 
							alt: "Product 1", 
							caption: "Premium Product Line - High quality materials with modern design aesthetics" 
						},
						{ 
							src: "https://placehold.co/800x500/10b981/ffffff?text=Product+2", 
							alt: "Product 2", 
							caption: "Eco-Friendly Collection - Sustainable materials for environmentally conscious consumers" 
						},
						{ 
							src: "https://placehold.co/800x500/f59e0b/ffffff?text=Product+3", 
							alt: "Product 3", 
							caption: "Limited Edition Series - Exclusive designs with premium features and finishing" 
						},
						{ 
							src: "https://placehold.co/800x500/ef4444/ffffff?text=Product+4", 
							alt: "Product 4", 
							caption: "Classic Collection - Timeless designs that never go out of style" 
						}
					]}
				/>

				<h3>Image Gallery</h3>
				<SwiperComponent
					slides={[
						{ 
							src: "https://placehold.co/800x500/8b5cf6/ffffff?text=Gallery+1", 
							alt: "Gallery Image 1", 
							caption: "Beautiful landscape photography capturing nature's finest moments" 
						},
						{ 
							src: "https://placehold.co/800x500/06b6d4/ffffff?text=Gallery+2", 
							alt: "Gallery Image 2", 
							caption: "Urban architecture showcasing modern design and innovation" 
						},
						{ 
							src: "https://placehold.co/800x500/84cc16/ffffff?text=Gallery+3", 
							alt: "Gallery Image 3", 
							caption: "Portrait photography highlighting human emotion and connection" 
						}
					]}
				/>
			</div>

			<h3>Features</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Smooth slide transitions and animations</li>
				<li>Touch-friendly swipe gestures for mobile</li>
				<li>Navigation arrows and pagination dots</li>
				<li>Keyboard navigation support</li>
				<li>Responsive design for all screen sizes</li>
				<li>Customizable slide content with captions</li>
				<li>Accessibility features for screen readers</li>
				<li>Auto-play functionality (optional)</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>Usage Example</h3>
			<pre><code>&lt;SwiperComponent
  slides={[
    { 
      src: "path/to/image1.jpg", 
      alt: "Image 1 description", 
      caption: "Caption for first slide" 
    },
    { 
      src: "path/to/image2.jpg", 
      alt: "Image 2 description", 
      caption: "Caption for second slide" 
    }
  ]}
/&gt;</code></pre>

			<h3>Slide Data Structure</h3>
			<p>Each slide should have the following structure:</p>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>src</strong>: URL or path to the image</li>
				<li><strong>alt</strong>: Alternative text for accessibility</li>
				<li><strong>caption</strong>: Descriptive caption displayed below the image</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>Use Cases</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Product galleries and showcases</li>
				<li>Portfolio presentations</li>
				<li>Testimonial carousels</li>
				<li>Image galleries and photo albums</li>
				<li>Feature highlights and announcements</li>
				<li>Before/after showcases</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>Interaction</h3>
			<p>Users can navigate through slides using:</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Navigation arrows (previous/next buttons)</li>
				<li>Pagination dots for direct slide access</li>
				<li>Touch gestures on mobile devices</li>
				<li>Keyboard arrow keys for accessibility</li>
			</ul>
		</section>
	</div>
</Layout>